&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Useful to analyse complete sleep cycles only (ensure incomplete cycles are excluded in the Common Settings for Sleep Cycles in the tool’s introduction step).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
