&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Useful to analyse NREM stages included in NREM periods only (not in REM periods). In this case, please check “Exclude REM periods”.&lt;/p&gt;
